channel.title: Need help with 562+
channel.description:
I have a problem running 562+. can someone help me to be able to run 614+ please ? i really want to try them they look nice. when i run them i get error_game_js5connect and the client stops at connecting to update server. I really want to try out newer versions but i cant so please help me :D
thanks.
